## Why This Is Asked

Assesses ability to operationalize exposure detection, policy enforcement, and rollback across accounts/regions using native AWS controls rather than ad hoc responses.

## Key Concepts

- AWS Config rules (managed/custom) for public exposure
- IAM Access Analyzer, and SCPs for cross-account access control
- EventBridge for workflow orchestration
- Lambda for automated remediation
- IaC drift testing and rollback mechanisms

